5. FORMAL VERIFICATION WITH TLA+

5.1 TLA+ Model Structure

```
--------------------- MODULE FM ---------------------
EXTENDS Integers, Sequences

CONSTANTS Tenants, Devices, Ports, Extents, MAX_RATE

VARIABLES owner, port_state, extent_owner, rate_counter, alloc_map

Init ==
  /\ owner \in [Devices -> Tenants ∪ {⊥}]
  /\ port_state \in [Ports -> {UP, DOWN}]
  /\ extent_owner \in [Extents -> Tenants ∪ {⊥}]
  /\ rate_counter \in [Tenants -> 0..MAX_RATE]
  /\ alloc_map \in [Tenants \X (Devices ∪ Extents) -> {0,1}]

Next ==
  \/ \E d \in Devices, t \in Tenants: Bind(d, t)
  \/ \E d \in Devices: Unbind(d)
  \/ \E e \in Extents, t \in Tenants: DCD_Add(e, t)
  \/ \E e \in Extents: DCD_Release(e)
  \/ \E p \in Ports: SetPortState(p, DOWN)
  \/ RateUpdate

\* Invariants
Confinement ==
  \A d \in Devices, t1, t2 \in Tenants:
    (owner[d] = t1 /\ alloc_map[t2][d] = 1) => t1 = t2
```

